Package com.hiddenswitch.spellsource.impl.util

Class UserRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hiddenswitch.spellsource.impl.util.MongoRecord
      • com.hiddenswitch.spellsource.impl.util.UserRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.vertx.ext.auth.User, java.io.Serializable
    public class UserRecord
extends MongoRecord
implements io.vertx.ext.auth.User, java.io.Serializable
    A user record.

    The fields in this object correspond to the ones stored in Mongo. This also implements the Vertx User interface, which allows queries to see if a user is authorized to do a particular task (very lightly implemented).
